snippet.title: NVIDIA VR Funhouse: Official Mods Trailer
snippet.description:
Step right up and play with new VR Funhouse Mods!  Learn More: http://www.geforce.com/whats-new/articles/funhouse-mods-available-now 

Swap out your shooting gallery pistols for a tommy gun, whack moles in 360 degrees, shoot colorful clowns with slow-motion goo, box moles with their hair on fire, and more!  With VR Funhouse mods the possibilities are endless.

Simply visit the VR Funhouse Steam Workshop page and download new mod experiences to add to your game.  You can also download the VR Funhouse Mod Kit, create your own mods, and share them with the world.

What are you waiting for?  Step right up and play with VR Funhouse mods today!
